        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Clarify if Pylon can bridge Slack-Teams communication for external partners.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=150.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [**Mismatched Needs:** Growthx requires a Slack-Teams federation broker for external partners; Pylon is an internal tool for consolidating channels within a single organization.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=321.0)\n  - [**Technical Blocker:** Pylon requires direct admin access to connect a Teams account, which is impossible for external partners.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=289.0)\n  - [**Prior Disqualification:** Growthx previously disqualified Pylon for a support platform use case, selecting Intercom instead.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=413.0)\n  - [**Action:** Nano will confirm the technical blocker and seek feedback on why Growthx chose Intercom, which helps Pylon's product evolution.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=648.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Growthx's Use Case: External Federation\n\n  - [**Goal:** Bridge communication with external partners whose security policies mandate Microsoft Teams.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=150.0)\n  - [**Requirement:** A federation broker to enable collaboration via shared channels/DMs without either party adopting the other's platform.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=150.0)\n  - [**Context:** This is a separate need from a support platform, for which Growthx selected Intercom.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=413.0)\n\n### Pylon's Capability: Internal Consolidation\n\n  - [**Primary Value:** Consolidate internal conversations from multiple platforms (Slack, Teams, email, WhatsApp) into one dashboard.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=341.0)\n  - [**Technical Requirement:** Requires direct admin access to connect a Teams account.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=289.0)\n  - [**Limitation:** This requirement makes it unsuitable for external federation, as Growthx cannot get admin access to a partner's Teams instance.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=289.0)\n\n### Prior Engagement & Feedback\n\n  - [**History:** Growthx colleagues (Leah, Andy, William) demoed Pylon in early December for a support platform use case.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=39.0)\n  - [**Outcome:** Growthx disqualified Pylon and selected Intercom.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=413.0)\n  - [**Pylon's Interest:** Nano requested feedback on the decision to inform product evolution.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=664.0)\n  - [**Competitor:** Growthx is also evaluating `conclude.io`.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=674.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [**Nano:** Confirm the technical blocker (need for external partner's Teams admin access) and seek feedback on why Growthx chose Intercom.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=648.0)\n  - [**Yousef:** Provide feedback on the Intercom decision if available.](https://fathom.video/share/-2iq1NvU8xkzFikF6J-8asds-wwWqK_w?tab=summary&timestamp=664.0)\n"
